OL,3,CPolice release 26-year-old man
OL,4,Carrested over Widdecombe murder
OL,6,FA 26-year-old man arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murdering former MP Ann
OL,8,FWiddecombe has been released from
OL,9,Fcustody and is no longer part of the
OL,10,Finvestigation, police said.
OL,12,FThe former minister was found dead at
OL,13,Fher home in Haytor on Dartmoor on
OL,14,FThursday, after sustaining serious
OL,15,Finjuries.
OL,17,FWiddecombe, who was 78, later became a
OL,18,FBrexit Party MEP and subsequently a
OL,19,FReform UK spokeswoman.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
