OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783916410
OL,3,CPolice release 26-year-old man
OL,4,Carrested over Widdecombe murder
OL,6,FOn Saturday, Devon and Cornwall Police
OL,7,Fconfirmed the man's release from
OL,8,Fcustody, following his arrest on
OL,9,FFriday.
OL,11,FAssistant Chief Constable Matt Longman
OL,12,Fsaid: "Our priority remains
OL,13,Fidentifying those responsible and
OL,14,Fensuring that all available evidence
OL,15,Fis thoroughly examined.
OL,26,@tD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
