PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783916410
OL,3,CPolice release 26-year-old man
OL,4,Carrested over Widdecombe murder
OL,6,F"Detectives continue to carry out
OL,7,Fnumerous enquiries as part of the
OL,8,Fongoing investigation and we remain
OL,9,Fcommitted to establishing the full
OL,10,Fcircumstances surrounding the
OL,11,Fincident."
OL,13,FHe said the investigation was "moving
OL,14,Fat a significant pace", adding: "We
OL,15,Fare deploying all of the necessary
OL,16,Fresources to find out exactly what has
OL,17,Fhappened.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@JO]uD@_OUvD@VO]vD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
