OL,3,CPolice release 26-year-old man
OL,4,Carrested over Widdecombe murder
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"I would appeal to anyone who may have
OL,12,Finformation about this incident,
OL,13,Fhowever insignificant it may seem, to
OL,14,Fcome forward and speak with us.
OL,16,F"We will release further information
OL,17,Fwhen we are able to do so. In the
OL,18,Fmeantime, I would ask people not to
OL,19,Fspeculate about what might have
OL,20,Fhappened, particularly on social media.
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
